     H            Y/
     F***************************************************
     F*  CREATE DOWNLOAD DATA TO PC(DC BZ QTY)
     F*                                                 *
     F***************************************************
     FAJSPW27 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAJSPL27 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAJSPL64 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAJSWP27 O   E           K        DISK                      A    UC
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    KEY     1   1 78
     E                    CMD     1   1 60
     E                    KB         15  3               MACHINE
     E                    KO         15  3               PROCESS
     E                    CHG        15 10 0             CHAGE DATE
     E                    ORC        15  3               PROCESS
     E                    OCN        15  3               MCN
     E                    QTY         2  7 0
     E                    MCN         2  3
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  45 KB
     I                                        1   3 CKKB01
